CRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"2d4d47b9df","type":"paragraph","text":"⑧代表人民利益的人，掌握人民武装力量，监督政权机构，保证社会主义道路。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"3b2b6d6fb2","type":"paragraph","text":"评语：只有认真整风才能救党，必须内外撤墙方有前途。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"b3b674ef76","type":"paragraph","text":"“国家政策虽然错误不多，事情办得却有些不好。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"d139035c73","type":"paragraph","text":"①镇反应镇反革命，不该错杀安分人。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"7d8aadda1e","type":"paragraph","text":"②三反五反胡乱斗，只退高潮未除根。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"0ec04122e2","type":"paragraph","text":"③统购统销是对的，但该适当顾民生。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"6aca3cd5fa","type":"paragraph","text":"④生活水平大提高，只有政权和工人。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"cd5012701d","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤肃反运动太过火，自己干部也寒心。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"a3f62f92a4","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥普遍怀疑激烈斗，致使人人均自危。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"89fb92fab3","type":"paragraph","text":"⑦正义耿直渐疏远，势力小人得嚣尘。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"f57440128a","type":"paragraph","text":"⑧位高校重利又厚，上爬风气日益盛。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"353e612943","type":"paragraph","text":"⑨政治完全代人情，社会道德败坏根。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"8b74fcc97d","type":"paragraph","text":"⑩专讲方式与态度，专工一笑绝七情。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"9313ce95e1","type":"paragraph","text":"评语：新政党虽有不少措施，好办法并没全收好效果。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"746b724c14","type":"paragraph","text":"“降生廿五年，经历两个社会：","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"cdb0ae6773","type":"paragraph","text":"①四岁入道门，生来反革命。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"6b0512e712","type":"paragraph","text":"②父母要积钱，求学绝了望。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"ffe387af22","type":"paragraph","text":"③十四做新郎，被迫去他乡。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"38b5fbe028","type":"paragraph","text":"④街头流浪子，幸逢好心人。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"d2fd436140","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤病归吃人窑，耕种在田野。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"c3e173bb1f","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥入得图书馆，埋头读古文。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"e9490d63d3","type":"paragraph","text":"⑦身居桓武校，险些丧残生。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"796739373b","type":"paragraph","text":"⑧光明来临，欣然参军。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"c9cef75f3c","type":"paragraph","text":"⑨主持正义，新遭斗争。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"7c31fed754","type":"paragraph","text":"⑩抗美援朝，笔记见闻。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"a3f3bb8b71","type":"paragraph","text":"⑾因为交朋友，不告念北京。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"3323d9ef92","type":"paragraph","text":"⑿杂文三五篇，反党有罪证。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"d544afe58a","type":"paragraph","text":"⒀不讲道理，下狱定罪。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"d6a9666c16","type":"paragraph","text":"⒁肃反开始，嫌疑又生。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"6944848c2a","type":"paragraph","text":"⒂胡风小卒，处自死刑。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"8f3f9ce93e","type":"paragraph","text":"⒃真相大白，一语示歉。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"3049457e88","type":"paragraph","text":"⒄结论很妙，思想落后。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"0327221fe7","type":"paragraph","text":"⒅离队学习，依然歧视。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"a4a44aac98","type":"paragraph","text":"评语：旧社会受害者，新社会冷落人。”","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"68881b7a2b","type":"paragraph","text":"“耳闻目睹相比校，好坏，光暗自分明”","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"6ed59bcbe1","type":"paragraph","text":"①个人独裁比一党专政。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"2d4e938f90","type":"paragraph","text":"②武力竞迭比指名投票。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"f00b71dac5","type":"paragraph","text":"③特务组织比官僚机构。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"120ffa9550","type":"paragraph","text":"④手枪威胁比思想鉴定。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"ca964235e9","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤政治迫害比阶级歧视。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"5d2b8c67f6","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥空喊自由比分级平等。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"91dc2d0c4b","type":"paragraph","text":"⑦是亲皆任比非党不拔。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"2f767a272d","type":"paragraph","text":"⑧金钱万能比党证多用。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"6105f26d66","type":"paragraph","text":"⑨血腥屠杀比残酷斗争。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"c8fa88e0be","type":"paragraph","text":"⑩全民仇恨比普遍不满。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"},{"id":"c577f3978a","type":"paragraph","text":"评语：蒋匪帮反动透顶，共产党缺点多端。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e0899dfaba"}]